Package: shipdetectR
Type: Package
Title: Ship Detection in Satellite Radar Imagery
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Clemens Schömig <clemens.schoemig@stud-mail.uni-wuerzburg.de>
Maintainer: Clemens Schömig <clemens.schoemig@stud-mail.uni-wuerzburg.de>
Description: Tools to detect ships in radar imagery, including masking to water areas,
    thresholding for ship pixels, clustering, filtering, bounding box creation,
    and export of ship locations. Uses 'terra', 'sf', and 'raster' packages.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    terra,
    sf,
    raster
